": \"flight costs\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a spokesperson from Jardine Motors has offered drivers an insight into some of the moreunique lawsthat are enforced in France, stating that learning them canhelp drivers feel safe behind the wheel.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jardine Motors\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 462, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9986393393661951, \"rank\": 0.0007478340824701804, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a spokesperson\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"an insight\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"the moreunique\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"lawsthat\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"canhelp drivers\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"the wheel\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They explained: \\\"While driving in a foreign country may be daunting, it can also be one of the best ways of traversing France while experiencing all the country has to offer.\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9986393393661951, \"rank\": 0.0007478340824701804, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a foreign country\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"the best ways\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 646}, {\"ngram\": \"all the country\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With a responsible attitude, the necessary documentation and an awareness of French driving laws, you will be en route to Olympic gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9997538184630796, \"rank\": 0.00013246120345297626, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a responsible attitude\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the necessary documentation\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"an awareness\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"route\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 853}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Used car expert shares electric car on sale for \\u00a34,000 that's 'genuinely quick' First, Jardine Motors noted that the biggest difference between driving in France and the UK is the side of the road motorists must use, with the French travelling on the right.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jardine Motors\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9986393393661951, \"rank\": 0.0007478340824701804, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999056037767, \"rank\": 8.121800476708553e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Used car expert shares electric car\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"sale\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest difference\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"the UK\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"the side\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"the road motorists\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whilst most tourists are already well aware of this, the company also suggested it is important to remember that this could alter some driving scenarios.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most tourists\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"some driving scenarios\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In particular, driving on the right-hand side of the road means that motorists must go anti-clockwise around roundabouts.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the right-hand side\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"motorists\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"roundabouts\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, drivers must still give way to the right, as they would in the UK.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999056037767, \"rank\": 8.121800476708553e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drivers\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"way\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Drivers risk fine of up to \\u00a31,000 for sneezing behind the wheel Do not miss:UK drivers paying hundreds more for insurance in the most expensive region Do not miss:Best choices for used city cars are stylish and reliable but cost under \\u00a32,500 We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1572, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999056037767, \"rank\": 8.121800476708553e-08, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drivers\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the wheel\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"insurance\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"the most expensive region\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"Best choices\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"used city cars\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1689}, {\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1876}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy In addition, motorists planning on driving in France should also remember that speed limits are always measured in kilometres, rather than miles.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2032, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9986393393661951, \"rank\": 0.0007478340824701804, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"motorists\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"speed limits\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"kilometres\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"miles\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If it is possible, Jardine Motors advised that drivers should adjust their vehicle's digital instrument panel to display the speed in KPH, with instructions on how to do this printed in the owner's manual.\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jardine Motors\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jardine_Motors_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 2267, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/League_of_Communists_of_Croatia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8149003206